{"about_the_game":"Become the Guardian of the Abyss and lead the Great Migration to bring forth the next Crab God \ud83e\udd80 Use your growing knowledge and great power to command your loveable crab babies (Crablings) to restore your ocean domain and protect your successor\u2019s egg as you venture into the watery depths.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289390/extras/CrabGod-crablings-GIF1.gif?t=1736933601\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Grow Your Crabling Colony</h2>Raise your Crablings! Nurture their personalities and potential as they worship you, build mighty coral reefs, fend off threats, and collect food for the journey ahead. Name them. Upgrade them. Grow your unique colony and guide them with your mighty claw as they become the next generation of ocean caretakers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289390/extras/CrabGod-enviro-GIF2.gif?t=1736933601\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Lead the Great Migration</h2>It is time for a new Crab God to rise and protect the oceans and it is your job to lead a successful migration, taking your egg to the depths where it can hatch. Balance the growth of your colony with the safety of your egg, otherwise, you will need to return to the shallows and start the migration anew.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289390/extras/CrabGod-combat_GIF3.gif?t=1736933601\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cultivate a Vibrant Underwater Ecosystem</h2>Reintroduce a healthy and vibrant diversity back to the ocean, and protect it from predators seeking easy prey. Varied sea life will sustain your colony. Unlock new combinations of flora and fauna to create a beautiful underwater environment.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289390/extras/CrabGod-eco-GIF4.gif?t=1736933601\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Real World Change</h2>Working with dots.eco, your in-game progression will help contribute to actual ocean conservation efforts. As you cultivate the great reefs of the Crab God, you will also be helping to sustain the beautiful world environment that inspires games like ours.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289390/extras/CustomizationGif1b.gif?t=1736933601\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>!UPDATE!</strong> Crabling Customisation</h2>Make each of your precious Crablings unique by customising their color, accessories, tools and more! You can even unlock little fish buddies to keep them company as you play.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Night of Many","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2289390/76b6fae39bf9c966e920dbb53a16129e8de16591.jpg"},{"name":"Master Builder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2289390/90d577752379710df3b5827d70b4ed28cf17a24e.jpg"},{"name":"Nature God","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2289390/705be99ca19eb608bf48dc707dedbc005d66f2ed.jpg"},{"name":"Sea Shepherd","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2289390/1ad67bf13fffebecb219d60952979b9045f0fa28.jpg"},{"name":"Eco Warrior","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2289390/fc18d7b5d23c2ec30a8ac462e43f5f2b7ea3d62a.jpg"},{"name":"Eco Legend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2289390/7f5fafea36307077deb84d8265f8720660829e57.jpg"},{"name":"Favoured One","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2289390/3ef792a2eec162a2de9fbf3930830fb1b553f9be.jpg"},{"name":"Rapid Response","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2289390/831e7e48beef111be47078fc2e1e56d17e51a6ab.jpg"},{"name":"Career Change","path":"h